root: ^Through the window this time you see a Great White, but its clear now that something is seriously wrong. In the first place, its far too large, nearly the size of a whale. Is it the long lost Megaladon? You'd rather not stick around to find out.

^Thankfully, the creature isn't too interested in you. A good thing, too, as one look at its mouth reveal its teeth to be covered, in bones, guts and gristle...worst of all, some of it looks distinctly human...
